{"tid":1555114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【頂你越南人】隨口問個問題 搞到我流馬尿","createTime":"2019-09-09T08:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T08:04:34.000Z","uid":314856,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58bd7623b72acbc7dbc9de1dfa98be459fc36493","tid":1555114,"uid":314856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:39:02.000Z","msg":"前兩日懷住<span style=\"color: brown;\">好撚複雜</span>嘅心情返越南探親 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，玩就真係<span style=\"color: teal;\">冇乜心情</span>架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係叫做儘量同人講下香港嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/phongtraoduvanghongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphongtraoduvanghongkong%2F&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Bultf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=febe8a93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/phongtraoduvanghongkong/</a><br />\n見到之前有幾個人都提過呢個group，於是PM 問佢呢度有無連儂牆，跟住就有以下對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itX3S0G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitX3S0G.png&h=a450ed3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">佢話西貢有搞《十年》放映會</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLq1EFG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLq1EFG.png&h=5a60a14a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">河內有連儂牆，胡志明市就唔清楚</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTCGEFH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTCGEFH.png&h=fcdf450d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越南人都係受共產黨控制，無民主無自由，黨員好撚有錢人民就食緊屎  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n突然間一句<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><em>Heung Gon yan ga yau</em></span></span></strong>，叫我哋唔好沉<br />\n屌我聽到已經濕濕哋... <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQ9xMkJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQ9xMkJ.png&h=83f53142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越南人自細被洗腦，要愛黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但香港嘅示威俾到好多力量佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港嘅年輕人教識我哋點樣爭取真正嘅自由同民主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多越南年輕人大開眼界，呢個亦係我哋5年前雨傘果陣成立嘅目的 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><em>Hug Heung Gon yan, from Saigonese with love</em></span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><span style=\"color: maroon;\">屌你屌你屌你</span></em></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dad7742c1cf4861e1c31a61aad4ca0d66f7dde4","tid":1555114,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:58:40.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83115d7578ab